<h3><a name="aim">What is CB good for?</a></h3>
<p>
	computrer-beatz has three major colums:
	<ol>
		<li>
			<strong>Database: </strong>
			Here each registered user can create <em>Artists, Labels, Albums</em> and <em>Tracks</em> and 
