<h3><a name="account">Do I need an account?</a></h3>
<p>
	If you are not registered you are free to browse most of the content as well as listen to, download and 
	comment music released on computer-beatz. But thats it. Only registered users are able to comment on 
	the music database, rate the entries there and mark them as favourite. Of course messenging and groups 
	are available for registered users only.
</p>
